::KitKat::

She smiled to herself.  She could see that Stringtra like Quickstrike.  It 
was as plain as day.  She had Cheetor by the shoulders.
"You going to get the feet or is he going to help carry this bot."
She looked at Quickstrike. "I'd let us carry him.  Your foot doesn't look 
all that great.  You'd be better off just carrying yourself back to your 
base.  We can carry this one."
She readjusted her grip on Cheetors shoulder.
"Well, let's get going before stuff happens again."
